prompts.frontCover: A flat 2D minimalist illustration for a greeting card front, clean design with simple elegant shapes and a soft pastel color palette. The scene is humorous and charming, set against a plain cream-colored background. In the center, a cartoon illustration of Lao Lao (from the reference photo, left) is happily sitting on a comically large, squishy beanbag chair shaped like a Corgi butt. She wears a light blue sweatshirt and has a joyful expression, holding a party blower to her lips. A tiny, minimalist party hat sits jauntily on her head. Cartoon Jordan (from the reference photo, right), wearing a tan hoodie, stands beside the beanbag chair with a funny, slightly exasperated expression, holding a comically oversized slice of birthday cake with a single lit candle. Two small, cute cartoon Shiba Inu dogs with party hats are playfully leaping near the bottom of the beanbag chair. Centered above the illustration, the phrase "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in a dark charcoal color. The overall composition is clean, playful, and full of negative space.
